                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="2"> I examined Sally Clarke’s writing, noting the places she travelled to, the
                            origins of the dishes she created and her stories of collecting recipes from the strangers
                            she met all over the world. To reflect her stories, I designed the ingredient lists and
                            methods of each recipe to appear like found printed ephemera which are stuck, scrapbook-like
                            into the cookbook.
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
